---
import { DELIVERY_ZONES, NEARBY_ZONES, POSTAL_CODE_RANGE, SITE } from '../consts';
---

<section id="zonas" class="bg-stone-50 py-20 sm:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-accent-600">Entrega gratis</span>
      <h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-stone-900 sm:text-4xl">
        Zonas donde llegamos sin costo
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-stone-600">
        Llevamos tu pedido directo a la puerta de tu casa en <strong>Atizapán de Zaragoza</strong> y municipios vecinos. Cobertura principal en los códigos postales <strong>{POSTAL_CODE_RANGE.primary}</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-14 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <article class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-brand-100 sm:p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-600 text-white">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-stone-900">Zona principal</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-stone-500">Entrega gratuita el mismo día</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <ul class="mt-5 grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
          {DELIVERY_ZONES.map((zone) => (
            <li
              class:list={[
                'flex items-center justify-between gap-3 rounded-lg border px-3 py-2.5',
                zone.highlight
                  ? 'border-brand-300 bg-brand-50'
                  : 'border-stone-200 bg-stone-50',
              ]}
            >
              <span class="min-w-0">
                <span class="block truncate text-sm font-semibold text-stone-900">{zone.name}</span>
                {zone.highlight && (
                  <span class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-brand-700">Aquí estamos</span>
                )}
              </span>
              <span
                class:list={[
                  'shrink-0 rounded-full px-2 py-0.5 font-mono text-xs font-semibold',
                  zone.highlight
                    ? 'bg-brand-600 text-white'
                    : 'bg-white text-stone-700 ring-1 ring-stone-200',
                ]}
              >
                {zone.postalCode}
              </span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>

        <a
          href={`https://wa.me/${SITE.whatsapp}?text=${encodeURIComponent('Hola! Quisiera hacer un pedido a domicilio.')}`}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="mt-5 inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-brand-600 px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-white shadow-md shadow-brand-600/20 transition hover:bg-brand-700"
        >
          Pedir a domicilio por WhatsApp
        </a>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-stone-200 sm:p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent-500/10 text-accent-700">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
              <path d="M2 12h20M12 2a15 15 0 0 1 0 20M12 2a15 15 0 0 0 0 20"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-stone-900">Otras colonias cercanas</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-stone-500">Consulta cobertura y tiempos por WhatsApp</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <ul class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {NEARBY_ZONES.map((zone) => (
            <li class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-stone-100 py-1.5 pl-3 pr-1.5 text-sm text-stone-800">
              <span class="truncate">{zone.name}</span>
              <span class="shrink-0 rounded-full bg-white px-2 py-0.5 font-mono text-[11px] font-semibold text-stone-600 ring-1 ring-stone-200">
                {zone.postalCode}
              </span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>

        <p class="mt-5 text-sm text-stone-600">
          También hacemos entregas en <strong>Cuautitlán Izcalli</strong>, <strong>Tlalnepantla</strong> y otros municipios del norte del Estado de México. Si tu colonia no aparece en las listas, <strong>pregúntanos</strong>.
        </p>

        <a
          href={`https://wa.me/${SITE.whatsapp}?text=${encodeURIComponent('Hola! ¿Entregan en mi colonia? Mi dirección es…')}`}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="mt-5 inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-stone-300 bg-white px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-stone-800 transition hover:border-brand-400 hover:text-brand-700"
        >
          ¿Llegan a mi colonia?
        </a>
      </article>
    </div>

    <p class="mx-auto mt-10 max-w-3xl rounded-xl bg-white p-4 text-center text-xs text-stone-500 ring-1 ring-stone-200">
      Los tiempos de entrega varían según tu ubicación. Pedidos en la <strong>zona principal (CP {POSTAL_CODE_RANGE.primary})</strong> suelen entregarse el mismo día.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
